IF TEST = 1 { ASSIGN getDay = now.datepart('day') ASSIGN getMonth = "{now.datepart('month')}" ASSIGN getYear = now.datepart('year') ASSIGN WeekOfDay = "{getMonth}/{getDay}/{getYear}" ASSIGN BegWeekOfDayConv = WeekOfDay.asdate-6 ASSIGN BegWeekOfDayMonth = "{BegWeekOfDayConv.datepart('Month')}" ASSIGN BegWeekOfDayDay = BegWeekOfDayConv.datepart('day') ASSIGN BegWeekOfDayYear = BegWeekOfDayConv.datepart('year') ASSIGN count = 1 ASSIGN c3 = 1
}
ASSIGN startBWDC = "{BegWeekOfDayConv+C3}" ASSIGN getMonthOf = "{startBWDC.datepart('Month')}" ASSIGN getDayOf = startBWDC.datepart('day') ASSIGN getYearOf = startBWDC.datepart('year')
ASSIGN DailyOf = "ChatSupport\Solved_ToAgent_Count\{getYearOf}\{getMonthOf}\{getMonthOf}_{getDayOf}_{getYearOf}.txt"
